sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Validator
    participant Handler
    participant GameDomain as Game (Domain)
    participant SessionDomain as GameSession (Domain)
    participant DB
    participant Events

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/sessions
    Note right of Client: {gameId, players: [{name, order, color}]}

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(StartGameSessionCommand)

    Mediator->>Validator: Validate(command)
    Validator->>Validator: Check player count
    Validator->>Validator: Validate player order
    Validator->>Mediator: Validation passed ✓

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>DB: Find game by ID
    DB-->>Handler: Game found

    Handler->>GameDomain: Validate player count
    GameDomain->>GameDomain: Check MinPlayers ≤ count ≤ MaxPlayers
    GameDomain-->>Handler: Valid ✓

    Handler->>SessionDomain: GameSession.Create(gameId, players)
    SessionDomain->>SessionDomain: Set Status = Setup
    SessionDomain->>SessionDomain: Add players
    SessionDomain->>Events: Raise GameSessionStartedEvent

    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(session)
    DB-->>Handler: Session saved ✓

    Handler->>Events: Publish GameSessionStartedEvent

    Handler-->>Mediator: GameSessionDto
    Mediator-->>Endpoint: GameSessionDto

    Endpoint-->>Client: 201 Created
    Note left of Client: {id, gameId, status: "Setup", players: [...]}
